                    {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 2,
                        "content": "Installation Guide",
                        "level": 1
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 3,
                        "content": "Follow these steps to install IntraVox on your Nextcloud server. Installation takes about 5 minutes."
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "columns": 1,
                "backgroundColor": "",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 1,
                        "content": "Requirements",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 2,
                        "content": "Before you begin, verify your server meets the following requirements:\n\n| Component | Minimum | Recommended |\n|-----------|---------|-------------|\n| Nextcloud | 27.0 | 28.0+ |\n| PHP | 8.0 | 8.2+ |\n| Database | MySQL 8.0 | MariaDB 10.6+ |\n| Memory | 256 MB | 512 MB+ |"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "columns": 1,
                "backgroundColor": "var(--color-background-hover)",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 1,
                        "content": "Step 1: Download",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 2,
                        "content": "Download IntraVox via the Nextcloud App Store or manually:\n\n**Via App Store (recommended):**\n1. Go to Nextcloud Admin > Apps\n2. Search for \"IntraVox\"\n3. Click \"Download and enable\"\n\n**Manually:**\n```bash\ncd /var/www/nextcloud/apps\nwget https://github.com/intravox/releases/latest.tar.gz\ntar -xzf latest.tar.gz\n```"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "columns": 1,
                "backgroundColor": "",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 1,
                        "content": "Step 2: Enable",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 2,
                        "content": "Enable the app via the command line:\n\n```bash\nsudo -u www-data php occ app:enable intravox\n```\n\nOr via the web interface:\n1. Go to Settings > Apps\n2. Find IntraVox in the list\n3. Click \"Enable\""
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "columns": 1,
                "backgroundColor": "var(--color-background-hover)",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 1,
                        "content": "Step 3: Configuration",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 2,
                        "content": "Run the setup wizard:\n\n```bash\nsudo -u www-data php occ intravox:setup\n```\n\nThis creates:\n- The IntraVox groupfolder\n- Default homepage\n- Navigation structure\n- Initial configuration"
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "columns": 1,
                "backgroundColor": "",
                "widgets": [
                    {
                        "type": "heading",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 1,
                        "content": "Step 4: Add Users",
                        "level": 2
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 2,
                        "content": "Add users to the IntraVox group:\n\n1. Go to Users > Groups\n2. Select \"IntraVox Users\" or \"IntraVox Editors\"\n3. Add the desired users\n\n**Roles:**\n- **Users**: Read only\n- **Editors**: Read and edit\n- **Admins**: Full control"
                    }
                ]
            },
